Related: AGPL, General Public Law, General Public Lease, General Public License, GNU, GPLv2, GPLv3, left


Every GNU GPL is a Free as in Freedom Trade Agreement between object instance owners that causes new object users to gain source control.

The GNU General Public Law as published by the Personal Sovereignty Foundation is enforced over Physical Sources through private property law.

The GNU General Public License as published by the Free Software Foundation is enforced over Virtual Sources through copyright law.

The Free Source Foundation's GNU General Public Law was originally written by Lord AGNUcius for GNU MMacs.


